review_blob: Aavistuksen samea, kuparinvrinen olut melko pienell ja nopeasti katoavalla vaahdolla. Karamellisen makeassa tuoksussa mys hunajaa sek liev hedelmist humalan puraisua. Maku jatkaa samalla pehmen karamellisella linjalla. Hysteen kivaa kuivattavaa hedelmist humalointia. Keskitytelinen suutuntuma, aika pehme juotavaa. Ihan kelpo, alkoholi ei maistu kuten saman panimon vahvemmassa Riservassa, joten vaikka tm joiltain osin j isoveljen varjoon, on tm lopulta pisteytykseltn samaa tasoa.
Keskiruskea olut kohtalaisella, pitkn silyvll vaahtokerroksella. Tuoksu luumuinen, makean hedelminen. Maku pehmen hedelminen.
Hieman samea vaalean kullankeltainen olut vaahtoaa alussa runsaasti. Tuoksu viljaisen maltainen. Maku makean viljaisen maltainen, ei kuitenkaan kovin erikoinen.
Punertavanruskea samea olut pienehkll, mutta pitsi jttvll vaahdolla. Hedelminen, humalan katkeroittama ihan toimiva tuoksu. Maku hedelminen, greippinen, hieman katkera.
Punertavan samea lhes vaahdoton olut. Makea, hedelminen, marjainen. Ei alkoholia havaittavissa.
Tummanruskea samea vaahtoamaton olut. Paahteinen tuoksu, maku maltainen ja paahteinen.
Samea hailakankeltainen olut vaahtoaa alussa runsaasti, mutta vaahto katoaa pian kokonaan. Raikas hedelminen tuoksu. Maku katkeran hedelminen, hieman tunkkainen.
Samea tummankeltainen vaahtoamaton olut. Tuoksu viljainen, maltainen ja hedelminen. Maku hedelminen, viljainen, maltainen ja hieman alkoholinen.

Kirkas kuparinvrinen olut melko pienell ja nopeasti katoavalla vaahdolla. Tuoksu karamellisen makea, hieman alkoholinen, lisksi siit lytyy omenaa, sitrusta ja ehk liev aniksisuutta. Maku toffeinen, hedelminen, varsinkin omenainen ja loppupuoleltaan kevyesti kuivattavan humaloitu. Alkoholi tuntuu hieman lmmittvn yleisilmeen, suutuntuma keskitytelinen ja ehk liev vetisyys vaivaa. Barleywineminen makea ja omenainen kokonaisuus toimii joiltain osin, mutta hieman viel hakee uomiaan. Parhaita maistamiani italialaisia toki.

Sorry, in Finnish this time: Miltei musta, todella runsaasti vaahtoava olut. Vaahtoa j reiluhko kerros pitkksi aikaa oluen pinnalle ja mys pitsi j runsaasti. Tuoksu tumman maltainen, suklainen ja hieman ruisleipinen. Maku makean maltainen, suklainen, lakritsainen, aavistuksen kahvinen ja melko pitk tumman vivahteikas jlkimaku on toimiva. Todella onnistunut kokonaisuus nill prosenteilla.

Golden, clear colour with a magnificent big white head that poured out of the bottle right after opening it. Leaves a nice head. Aroma is malty and a bit citrus. Taste is nice with spice and citrus together with some malty and sweetness. Quite a surprise and very good Belgian Tripel.

Special beer you cant find from local shops. Light, a bit cloudy golden beer. Quite a lot foam. Light aroma, a bit fruity and grainy. Light taste with some bitter. A bit sloppy. Nothing special and as its difficult to get this beer, dont bother.

Speciality that you cant find in local shops. Light, a bit cloudy golden beer. Makes quite a lot foam. Light aroma, taste is soft and sweet. Palate is average. Citrus tastes more and more while coming to the end.
With this availability, the price is high and the beer is not worth it.

A large charm of this beer comes from a very special hourglass that this beer is served. Luckily I have that particular glass to enjoy the beer as its authentic style. Foam is very strong. A bit red brown beer with a very sweet aroma. Also taste includes a lot of sweetness but not too much. Nice beer to enjoy.
A long time favorite. Works fine in a bar, at home, while eating, after sauna, at terrace etc.
Cloudy, a bit orange colour with a small head. Quite interesting as whole.

Dark brown beer pours in its own glass with a moderate but long lasting head. I had a lot of expectations beforehand and this beer managed to answer to these expectations. This beer really has a quality. Its almost perfect.
A better part of finnish "bulkkiolut" genre. Suits fine after sauna or when you are thirsty, but nothing special or interesting.
One example of the finnish "bulkkiolut" genre. After sauna or while drinking for thirsty, but otherwise do not choose this one.

Pale yellow, a bit cloudy beer with a large, light head. Aroma is a bit floral and citrus. Delicious, sweetly fruity taste. Finish is a bit alcoholic but not too much. Palate is average and sparkling.

Dark brown, almost black colour with a small head. Aroma is full, malty, a bit yeasty, smoky (smoked ham). Sweet and soft taste includes juniper and smoke. Finish is long. One of the best finnish beers.

Black beer with a strong brown head. Aroma is sugar and coffee but the main profit comes from the taste. Its almost perfect including dark chocolate, coffee (just right amount) and sweetness. Finish is bitter, burned malty and coffee. Just wonderful beer and easy to drink.
Light golden "beer" with a minimum head. Aroma is light and taste is even more light. Just like drinking some bad sparkling water.

Very light yellow as a colour, cloudy. Head is rich but fades away quickly. Aroma is mild and taste is light with some citrus. Carbonation is average. Works fine with hot summer terraces or after sauna, but you can find so many better hefes that Im not going to buy this anymore.
Dark brown, cloudy beer with a big head that fades away quickly. Aroma is banana so as is taste. Body is too light and sloppy.

I have always liked Gouden Carolus beers and this one makes no difference. Dark brown beer with a big head. Nice aroma includes anise and malty caramel. Taste is also sweet but not too sweet. Works perfectly with a lamb.
Almost legendary Belgian beer. Vary famous itself. I had tasted this earlier, but this time was in a local bar from its own glass. Very tasty, includes both bitter and sweetness. Wonderful beer.
In a bar. Dark colour, sweet but not tasty enough. This beer is easy to drink but should have much more special and taste to be better.
Large white head. Golden beer with some citrus and sweetness. Taste is also sweet. Body is full.
Large white head that disappears quickly. Golden beer with minimum aroma. Easy to drink, refreshing, light but still enough taste.
Some fruits and banana in taste. Refreshing beer for summer time but not in the top of wheat beers.
Black beer with a minimum head. Taste is toasty including coffee and chocolate. One of the best finnish beers.
Golden beer with aroma of banana and yeast. Medium palate; carbonic. Taste includes yeast, wheat and banana. Good wheat beer.
Good wheat beer but nothing special. There are better options available. That one is good in hot summer terraces.
Deep dark brown colour. A lot of foam that stays long. Sweet aroma. Taste is medium, sweet, soft, a bit spicy afterwards.
This beer has everything that is needed. Pours beautifully, gives a nice foam, aroma is wonderful, tastes strong enough with multiple different aromas. After Westy 12 best Quadrupel so far.
One of the best hefeweissbiers. Enough taste, enough aroma. Very nice in some summer terrace.
Good trappist. Dark brown with quite small head/foam. Anise is major in aroma. Also taste includes anise, caramel and some sweetness.

Orange/brown colour with some head. Aroma is wonderful with some caramel and fruits. Taste includes some bitterness and caramel sweetness. Finish is a bit bitter but should last longer.

Nice "trappist".
